"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Howdy folks. Got a few people asking in our [Plebs discord](https://discord.gg/plebs) how to avoid losing your very precious Ether with failed transactions, whether that’s minting, swapping, or any other interactions.\\n\\n> *“plebs help plebs”*\\n\\n## Using Flashbots Protect\\n\\n### Benefits:\\n\\n* **Frontrunning protection** - we get to avoid bots that try to scalp our swaps/trades\\n* **Priority in blocks** - we’re mined at the top of blocks, letting you get confirmed faster than normal transactions being sent to the main mempool\\n* **No failed transactions** - transaction only mined if it goes through, no losing gas fees!\\n\\nWhat you’re probably used to seeing when doing crypto stuff on your pc is MetaMask, and being plugged into the Ethereum Mainnet for whatever you’re up to:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/puB3JcgL1AfXbZlZtxCTN.jpg?height=104&width=351)\\n\\nWhat we’ll be doing is using the Flashbots RPC to send our transactions through, instead of the normal, public, Ethereum Mainnet that everyone is usually connected to.\\n\\n*Note - you don’t have to buy anything, transfer any funds, or do anything like that. All you’re doing is switching your ‘network’ and telling MetaMask who to direct your transaction towards.*\\n\\n### Setting It Up\\n\\n1. Open your MetaMask extension, and click on the top where you see ‘Ethereum Mainnet’ and select ‘Custom RPC’\\n2. Add ‘Flashbots RPC’ as the Network Name\\n3. Add *https://rpc.flashbots.net* as the RPC URL\\n4. Set the Chain ID as 1. MetaMask might tell you it’s already being used but you can ignore that\\n5. Set your currency as *ETH*\\n6. Click Save\\n\\nAnd just like that, you’ve got yourself linked up to the Flashbots Protection RPC. Keep in mind, this is still the Ethereum Mainnet, all you’re doing is using a specific node to get your transactions confirmed, instead of submitting it to the open, public mempool where the bots and miners are all competing. \\n\\nHope this helps! \\n\\nFollow [my Twitter](https://twitter.com/Mona_La_Vinci) \\n\\n[https://twitter.com/Mona_La_Vinci](https://twitter.com/Mona_La_Vinci)\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/Mona_La_Vinci/status/1446985698750332928](https://twitter.com/Mona_La_Vinci/status/1446985698750332928)\\n\\nJoin the Plebs:\\n\\n[https://discord.gg/svsWe7DVVN](https://discord.gg/svsWe7DVVN)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1634343701,\"title\":\"Guide: Don't lose money with failed transactions\"},\"digest\":\"oL9du4cpbFPl6lNfJ8ZEIO5dci7zRJaYLOYTHq0hctk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9A84915DFf8F8801b26D0b35b199E5C16E29f899\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ic1tu6skZgrxMXenf53IO1c16X2almA4rFMuDL_63_M\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"q5nYdB2UZ1RnThfrq_jOkfh4y3AAzrQ10Fx66pCTKe8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"of2wDmL4hWDY7o5bRdCYPKoBeIfjUZEuvrllULGoMDtEodGqP31sO3EX7lQ_fy0d_QQm8Dn6cI2HOGZnW4mP9A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x8e6da63fdcd07cd02c2d12c3a77f32cf02c9900b16a84846a0ece8701398706a2d63add0646bf1feb211e41beda67b579a3bb88bcc8b6782ebac051a8c73f09a1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ic1tu6skZgrxMXenf53IO1c16X2almA4rFMuDL_63_M\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"q5nYdB2UZ1RnThfrq_jOkfh4y3AAzrQ10Fx66pCTKe8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"oL9du4cpbFPl6lNfJ8ZEIO5dci7zRJaYLOYTHq0hctk\"}"